  SelectedLvlDescription: {fileID: 751680392}
  Names:
  - Hold me tight
  - Violent response
  - Weft & Warp
  - Crimson Dusk
  - Eternal Sunshine
  - Loop&Loop
  Descriptions:
  - Oh, I sing while thinking of you.
  - Though some confilicts are unavoidable, it's best to not pick up unnecessary
    fights.
  - "At its heart, weaving is the simple\u2014but powerful\u2014act of interlacing
    two sets of threads: warp and weft. The warp threads are stretched vertically
    on a loom, while the weft threads are woven side-to-side, creating a strong,
    balanced fabric."
  - Sometimes, a seemingly unconventional solution turns out to be the most suitable
    one.
  - If the sun is way too far from reach, might as well making your own.\n<color=yellow>Swap
    cool-down is halved in this level.</color>
  - '"You see, life is all about turning back."\n<color=yellow>Your units have increased
    max HP and MSPD in this level.</color>\n<color=red>The ''Sudarim'' are immune
    to damage from Originium Pollutions.</color>'
  ChallengeModes:
  - Terrains and enemies will differ in places, and more enemies will appear.
  - Bloodboil Knightclub Elite's ability stacks twice as fast. All enemies have increased
    MSPD.
  - One Sentinel has their position changed and takes different route. All 'Sentinels'
    have increased MSPD.
  - All enemies become immune to physical and magical damage. 'Originiutants' have
    increased ASPD.
  - Some 'Originium Pollutions' will appear beforehand. 'Sudarim' are immune to damage
    from 'Originium Pollution'.
  - One 'Sudaram' has different starting position.
